{"TopicId":196103,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Looking for a mod that automatically turn off throttle and RCS when landed or docked.","CreatedByName":"RandomKerbal","CreatedById":206026,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-04T14:41:51Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"RandomKerbal","CreatedById":206026,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-04T14:41:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRecently, I have encountered problems such as the X on my keyboard is not sensitive anymore, causing my landers\u00A0to bounce and flew back into sub-orbit as they land.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anyone know a mod/plugin that automatically turn off the\u00A0engines immediately when your spacecraft touches the surface of a planet?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-23T04:24:53Z\u0022 title=\u002208/23/2020 04:24  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 23, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by RandomKerbal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-04T14:54:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/206026-randomkerbal/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022206026\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/206026-randomkerbal/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@RandomKerbal\u003C/a\u003E mebbe this?\u003Cbr\u003E\nuse a fuel flow part, and an altitude part, set to 1m or 0m, to cut fuel flow, and the engine will just flameout? vOv\u003Cbr\u003E\nOr mebbe the altitude part alone can deactivate the engine at set altitude?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u00